msItem.title: La rivoluzione in Francia ed in Italia
msItem.author: Font. , Francesco

supportDesc.extent: 379 leaves : 267 x 190 mm. bound to 274 x 197 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, i + 379 + i; 1-166, [iv], 167-375, 377-457, 558-855; contemporary pagination in ink, upper outer corners; 2 preliminary leaves cut out, one of these presumably was a title.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in a cursive script by a single hand, with two unnumbered leaves between p. 166-167 in a different hand.

binding.p: Contemporary half calf, with title on spine and legend "Tom. I. MSS."
